 of the Washington Post;\nMrs. Mary Louise Simon of the Re\ntraining and Re-employment Ad\nministration. Labor Department:\nDeWitt C. Smith of the American\nRed Cross, and G Howland -Shaw,\nformer Assistant Secretary of State.\nChailes P. Taft, nationally known\nLIABILITY INSURANCE\nand all forms of insurance j\nIncluding LIFE\nR>\\ RJ V\nREALTORS\nover HO year*' eiprritne*\n7 41 10th St. N.W. N A 076-V\ni\na\nGLASSES\nWITH\nEXAMINATION\nOFFICE HOURS\n9 A M. TO 6 P.M.\nMonday Thro Saturday\ns ,?J97S\nBAR STYLE FRAME, S3.00 ADDITIONAL\nBIFOCALS, S3.00 ADDITIONAL\nHIHEIEYENTYFIYE\n932 F St. N.W. 4\u20142nd Floor\nMetropolitan Theater Building\nUptown Address\u201419T1 14th St. N.W\nFREE PARKING\u2014STAR PARKING PLAZA\u2014 l\u00abth and E N.W.\nNow Available\nSTEEL SLAT\nEnclosed Head\nVENETIAN BLINDS\nMay We Estimate?\nTHE SHADE SHOP\nForty-fifth year in Business\n830 13th St. N.W. RE, 6262\nZone 5\nVV. StoR.es Sommers\n200,000 Square Feet in Stock\u2014NO WAITING!\nKENTILE\nTr\u00ab4\u00bb Nnk Rtf.\nThe only floor with a direct factory\nguarantee against curling or buckling.\nFactory Pre-waxed\nCemented direct\nto concrete\n200 Square Feet\n$17.95\n\u201cCompletely\nInstalled\nSlightly more tor\ninstallation on wood\nBeautiful Marbleized Colors for\nRecreation Rooms or Any Room in the House\nHood Rubber Tile, Cork Tile by Kentile for\nResiliency and Quietness\nPennsylvania Linoleum Co.\n921 G St. N.W. Free Estimates Dl. 5614\nattorney, civic and welfare leaderi\nof Chicago, has accepted the nom\nination for president of the new\norganization and will be principal\nspeaker at the luncheon which fel\nlows the business session.\nThe National Social Welfare As\nsembly marks the joining of forces\non the part of 35 national organiza\ntions.\nDr. Samuel J. Dantzic\n\u2014Optometritt\nScientific\nEye Examination\nServing discriminating Woshingtomonj\nfor over a quarter of a century.\nComplete Laboratory Facilities\nfor Designing and Making Glasses.\nFor Appointment Call EX 5546\n625 15th St. N.W.\n1 boors From Keith's Theater)\nAUTO SEAT\nCOVERS\nREADY\nMADE\nOR\nCUSTOM\nTAILORED\nAuto Glass\nPromptly Installed\nAuto Seat Cover Co.\n1809 14th St. N.W. DU. 2796\nEvery Little Forkful\nHas a Meaning\nof Its Own:\nTonight's Dinner Special\nROAST STI FFED LONG ISLAND\nDUCKLING. \\PPLF oc\nSAUCE Appetizer \u00abw0\nto dessert\nFeaturing Hone Made\nDesserts Daily\nDinner. 5 to 9 P.M.\nLafayette\n\u2022\u2022\u2022Room\n18th and Eve Sts. N.W.\nU COCKTAIL LOUNGE 1\nSocially satisfying quietude\nSPECIAL\namong a wide choice jor\ndinner tonight:\nLOBSTER 5*00\nNEWBURGH\naccompanied\u2014as always\u2014b*\nHot Home Made Cornsticks\nand\nHome Made Desserts\nserved in rhe unusual!*\ncomfortable socially\nenjoyable a mospnere\nthat individualizes\nThe Parrot\nRESTAURANT\nConn. Are. at R St\nFREE PARKING\nWANTED!\nYoung Men and Women for\nExecutive and Supervisory\nPositions\nEarn $65 to $125 a Week!\nOnly those accustomed to earning that amount\nneed apply. Men and women with ambition and\npersonality offered unusual opportunity. College\ntrained people between 25 and 35 given preference.\nDo not telephone or write. Personal interview only.\nApply at once!\nARTHUR MURRAY DANCE STUDIOS\n1101 Connecticut Avenue\nHOUSES WANTED\nFor Sale or Rent\u2014Furnished or Unfurnished\nHOL ED you wish to Sell or Rent your\nhouse we can be of service to you if\nyou will list it with us.\ne have numerous requests for City,\nSuburban and Country Properties.\nRAXDALL II. n.VGNKK COMPANY\nReal Estate\nSALES RENTALS LOANS INSURANCE\n1321 Connecticut Avenue N.W. Telephone: DEcatur 3600\nProperty Management\nCalls for a\nThe management of property,\nwhether it is a home, store, apart\nment or office building, should be\nhandled by competent and experi\nenced realtors. Shannon Luchs\nCo., with a 40-year background and\na thorough knowledge of real estate\nprocedures, has specialists to assist\nyou in managing your property\nin making new leases, supervising\nrepairs, hiring service employes and\nmany other details. Let Shannon\nLuchs Co. take these problems\noff your hands.\nComplete Reol Estate Service Since 1906\nREALTORS\n1505 H Street N.W. NAtional 2345\nMember ot Institute bt Rent Estate Mcnapement\nJust one hour with Arthur Murray's\nMAGIC STEP\nwill start you dancing\nHEN Arthur Murray made\nthe startling discovery\nthat all modern dances are\nbased on this one simple step\nhe found the way to make you\nan expert dancer in a few short\nhours.\nEven after one hour's lesson\nyou can make a date to go\ndancing. You\u2019ll have the Fox\nTrot rhythm in your toes\u2014and\nyou\u2019ll actually do some trick\nvariations\n/('i Fun Learning\nYes\u2014dancing comes as easy\nas breathing when we show\nyou the clue. Arthur Murray\u2019s\naccomplished teachers bring out\nyour hidden talent. The Fox\nTrot\u2014with all its latest steps\n\u2014seems like child's play. You\ncan do the sophisticated Rumba\nafter a few delightful lessons.\nConfidence grows like magic,\nyou learn so fast.\nSo Popular\u2014So Gay!\nRight now put yourself in\nour hands. Become a popular\npartner discover new gaiety,\npoise, relaxation you never\ndreamed of before. Good\ndancers always get tbe cream\nof the fun Join them at your\nnext party.\nNow't the Time to Learn\nToday phone the Studio (EXec.\n4100) and make your date for\nlessons. Or come and talk it\nover.\nLOOKS\n~EASy/\nTry it\nyourself\nIf you can do this simpta\nst*p Arthur Murray\nteachers can make von\nan expert dancer in\nfew hours!\nETHEL FIST ERE, Director\nARTHUR MURRAY noTSUilw\nK k","height":"31496","width":"22428"}}
